summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 5525 for the improvement of The Alley in Block 1, Cove Addition to Seattle, being the alley between Queen Anne Avenue and 1st Avenue North, from Boston Street to McGraw Street; by paving and otherwise improving the same; under Ordinance No. 70780, and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
